{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-markdown-post-js","path":"/fluxstore/multi-language/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://docs.inspireui.com","title":"InspireUI Document","description":"InspireUI document"}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Multi-language, including RTL","date":null,"date_pretty":null,"path":null,"meta_title":"FluxStore - Universal mobile commerce Flutter app for Magento, WooCommerce and Opencart","meta_description":"Fluxstore is universal app that fully integration with the Woocommerce, Mangeto and Opencart","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"fluxstore","toc":null,"keywords":["fluxstore","flutter app","fluxstore","Magento app","Woo Commerce app","Opencart app"]},"html":"<p>This section show how to config Language, Country Code, Symbol, Currency, Google font.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1*elmUADc6HzKE8Zuf9-BSRw.gif\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>On WooCommerce, to support for translating the product content (title, description..), it is required to install the following plugins: </p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-multilingual\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">WooCommerce Multilingual</a>. </li>\n<li>WPML Multilingual CMS</li>\n<li>WPML String Translation +2.0</li>\n<li>WPML Translation Management +2.2</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If your website don’t use WPML, it is possible to integrate with <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/polylang/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Polylang</a> plugin.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>From version 1.7.x, there are more than 10 languages in the app: English, Vietnam, Japanese, Chinese, Indonesiana, Spanish, Arabic, Romanian, Turkish, Italian, German, Portuguese, Brazil, French...  You also can add/edit/delete languages.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ebc455df5cd1d8829b4ceb10495ed5fe/582e9/0_3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"fluxstore-1\"\n        title=\"fluxstore-1\"\n        src=\"/static/ebc455df5cd1d8829b4ceb10495ed5fe/29d74/0_3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ebc455df5cd1d8829b4ceb10495ed5fe/b4ec0/0_3.png 200w,\n/static/ebc455df5cd1d8829b4ceb10495ed5fe/24144/0_3.png 400w,\n/static/ebc455df5cd1d8829b4ceb10495ed5fe/29d74/0_3.png 800w,\n/static/ebc455df5cd1d8829b4ceb10495ed5fe/5c837/0_3.png 1200w,\n/static/ebc455df5cd1d8829b4ceb10495ed5fe/582e9/0_3.png 1400w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-add-or-update-language\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#how-to-add-or-update-language\" aria-label=\"how to add or update language permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to add or update language?</h2>\n<p>To add a new language, please follow step below:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <code class=\"language-text\">lib/l10n/</code> the folder and copy the existing files to make a new one (you may see there are many languages demo from the app). Let’s take adding the new French (fr) Language for example, the format should be <code class=\"language-text\">intl_fr.arb</code>. We suggest using the Android Studio with <strong><a href=\"https://plugins.jetbrains.com/plugin/13666-flutter-intl\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Flutter Intl</a></strong> when inputting new language to support auto-generating the WidgetsLocalizations file <code class=\"language-text\">lib/generated/i10n.dart</code>.</li>\n<li>Go to <code class=\"language-text\">lib/common/tools.dart</code>  and update the list from <code class=\"language-text\">getLanguagesList</code> function </li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"dart\"><pre class=\"language-dart\"><code class=\"language-dart\">  <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">Function</span> getLanguagesList <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>context<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> context <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span> <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> S<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">of</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>context<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>english <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"English\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"icon\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> ImageCountry<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>GB<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"code\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"text\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"English\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"storeViewCode\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> context <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span> <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> S<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">of</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>context<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>vietnamese <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Vietnam\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"icon\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> ImageCountry<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>VN<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"code\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"vi\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"text\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Vietnam\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"storeViewCode\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// ....</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Go to <code class=\"language-text\">lib/common/constants/images.dart</code> and update the language flag image</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"dart\"><pre class=\"language-dart\"><code class=\"language-dart\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ImageCountry</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> String GB <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'assets/images/country/gb.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> String VN <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'assets/images/country/vn.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">//...</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Add new JSON file to support for the config the layout homepage, for more detail guideline please check the <a href=\"/fluxstore/home-layout/#2-home-layout\">Layout &#x26; Theming</a>) guide.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token comment\">// lib/config/config_xx.json (with `xx` is language)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"HorizonLayout\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"layout\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"logo\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"showMenu\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"showSearch\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"showLogo\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"background\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"#FFFFFF\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t  <span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"default-language--curency\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#default-language--curency\" aria-label=\"default language  curency permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Default Language &#x26; Curency</h2>\n<p>Open <strong><code class=\"language-text\">lib/common/config/general.dart</code></strong> file and update the <code class=\"language-text\">DefaultCurrency</code> section. </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\">const kAdvanceConfig = <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"DefaultLanguage\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"DefaultCurrency\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"symbol\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\\$\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"decimalDigits\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"symbolBeforeTheNumber\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"currency\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"USD\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"currencyCode\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"usd\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"smallestUnitRate\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 100 cents = 1 usd</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  ...\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>;</code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"multi-currencies-setting\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#multi-currencies-setting\" aria-label=\"multi currencies setting permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Multi Currencies Setting</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/5dbd9/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter\"\n        title=\"fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter\"\n        src=\"/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/29d74/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/b4ec0/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png 200w,\n/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/24144/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png 400w,\n/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/29d74/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png 800w,\n/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/5c837/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png 1200w,\n/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/db573/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png 1600w,\n/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/5dbd9/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png 2880w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>This feature is only available for WooCommerce version, below is required condiction to active this feature:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Update the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mstore-api/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">mstore-api</a> to latest version <strong>v1.5.4.</strong></li>\n<li>Add new setting from Manage Currencies from WPML plugin:</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/0e5af/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 37%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"IMG_1790fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui\"\n        title=\"IMG_1790fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui\"\n        src=\"/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/29d74/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/b4ec0/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png 200w,\n/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/24144/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png 400w,\n/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/29d74/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png 800w,\n/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/5c837/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png 1200w,\n/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/db573/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png 1600w,\n/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/0e5af/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png 2284w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Open the Fluxstore project, and update the <code class=\"language-text\">lib/common/config/general.dart</code> and update the <code class=\"language-text\">Currencies</code> value</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\">const kAdvanceConfig = <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  ...\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"Currencies\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"symbol\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\\$\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"decimalDigits\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"symbolBeforeTheNumber\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"currency\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"USD\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"symbol\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"đ\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"decimalDigits\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"symbolBeforeTheNumber\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"currency\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"VND\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>;</code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"multi-shipping-countries--states\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#multi-shipping-countries--states\" aria-label=\"multi shipping countries  states permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Multi Shipping Countries &#x26; States</h2>\n<p>To limit the country list from the Shipping Address screen, open <code class=\"language-text\">lib/common/config.dart</code> and update the DefaultCountry (From version 1.6.5 onwards, open <strong>lib/common/config/payments.dart</strong>). </p>\n<p>Example: if you would like to display on 3 countries, configure as below:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\">const List DefaultCountry = <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Vietnam\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"iosCode\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"VN\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"icon\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://cdn.britannica.com/41/4041-004-A06CBD63/Flag-Vietnam.jpg\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"India\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"iosCode\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"IN\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"icon\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/41/Flag_of_India.svg/1200px-Flag_of_India.svg.png\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token property\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Austria\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token property\">\"iosCode\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"AT\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token property\">\"icon\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>;</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/363b05d8fb7362b81b7cf2c307ede569/70336/default-shipping.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Screen Shot 2020-06-11 at 09.49.05\"\n        title=\"Screen Shot 2020-06-11 at 09.49.05\"\n        src=\"/static/363b05d8fb7362b81b7cf2c307ede569/29d74/default-shipping.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/363b05d8fb7362b81b7cf2c307ede569/b4ec0/default-shipping.png 200w,\n/static/363b05d8fb7362b81b7cf2c307ede569/24144/default-shipping.png 400w,\n/static/363b05d8fb7362b81b7cf2c307ede569/29d74/default-shipping.png 800w,\n/static/363b05d8fb7362b81b7cf2c307ede569/5c837/default-shipping.png 1200w,\n/static/363b05d8fb7362b81b7cf2c307ede569/db573/default-shipping.png 1600w,\n/static/363b05d8fb7362b81b7cf2c307ede569/70336/default-shipping.png 2856w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p> ⚠️ Note: To update <strong>the States</strong> list of your country, add new state file. E.g.: to display State/Province for India, add the state file below:</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a8a67ce237545fb4a0d2dd09eaddbe41/c9875/state.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image1\"\n        title=\"image1\"\n        src=\"/static/a8a67ce237545fb4a0d2dd09eaddbe41/29d74/state.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a8a67ce237545fb4a0d2dd09eaddbe41/b4ec0/state.png 200w,\n/static/a8a67ce237545fb4a0d2dd09eaddbe41/24144/state.png 400w,\n/static/a8a67ce237545fb4a0d2dd09eaddbe41/29d74/state.png 800w,\n/static/a8a67ce237545fb4a0d2dd09eaddbe41/5c837/state.png 1200w,\n/static/a8a67ce237545fb4a0d2dd09eaddbe41/db573/state.png 1600w,\n/static/a8a67ce237545fb4a0d2dd09eaddbe41/c9875/state.png 1788w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"multi-google-fonts\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#multi-google-fonts\" aria-label=\"multi google fonts permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Multi Google Fonts</h2>\n<p>Flutter 1.2.x come with powerful Google Font library, you can load any font from google font and load to your app dynamically without downloading to the assets folder.</p>\n<p>If you add more languages to the app and would like to change the font family, go to <code class=\"language-text\">lib/common/constants.dart</code> (From version 1.6.5 onwards, go to <strong>lib/common/config/fonts.dart</strong>)</p>\n<p>Example: add new <code class=\"language-text\">fr</code> language with <strong>Lato</strong> font:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"dart\"><pre class=\"language-dart\"><code class=\"language-dart\"><span class=\"token comment\">///Google fonts: https://fonts.google.com/</span>\nTextTheme <span class=\"token function\">kTextTheme</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>theme<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> String language<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">switch</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>language<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token string\">'vi'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> GoogleFonts<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">montserratTextTheme</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>theme<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token string\">'ar'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> GoogleFonts<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">ralewayTextTheme</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>theme<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token string\">'fr'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> GoogleFonts<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">latoTextTheme</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>theme<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> GoogleFonts<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">ralewayTextTheme</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>theme<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nTextTheme <span class=\"token function\">kHeadlineTheme</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>theme<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>language <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'en'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">switch</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>language<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token string\">'vi'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> GoogleFonts<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">montserratTextTheme</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>theme<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token string\">'ar'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> GoogleFonts<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">ralewayTextTheme</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>theme<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> GoogleFonts<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">ralewayTextTheme</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>theme<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>If you don’t want to use Google Font and only use Custom Font Type, please refer to the guide from <a href=\"https://flutter.dev/docs/cookbook/design/fonts\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Flutter Document.</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Note: When installing, if you get issue, please go to <a href=\"https://docs.inspireui.com/fluxstore/common-question/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Common Questions</a> and <a href=\"https://docs.inspireui.com/fluxstore/common-issues/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Common Issues</a> to get Customer key, Consumer secret,... and to see the list of common issues and solutions to fix it.</p>\n</blockquote>","fields":{"slug":"/fluxstore/multi-language/"},"timeToRead":5,"excerpt":"This section show how to config Language, Country Code, Symbol, Currency, Google font. img On WooCommerce, to support for translating the…","fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/minh/Data/Projects/web/inspireui-document/content/fluxstore/multi-language.md"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/fluxstore/multi-language/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}